title: Bread Machine Garlic Bread
ingredients: ['225ml (8 fl oz) warm water (45 C)', '1 tablespoon butter', '1 tablespoon dried milk powder', '1 tablespoon caster sugar', '1 1/2 teaspoons salt', '1 1/2 tablespoons dried parsley', '2 cloves garlic, minced and crushed into a paste', '400g (14 oz) bread flour', '2 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
